</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_83" id="41v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Seyfrid und Friczen Lwchner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wiszt, <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Seyfrid und Fricz Lewchner, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie wir ewch in
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz ir bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        scheden gewest seyt und <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eins geleyts zu uns
                        begert, ewch des zu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn ir
                                <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> heyligen tag nehst</q>01.11.1414</note></app> zu uns kombt und des
                        begert, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch zu uns und von uns, für
                        uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, <add>und bey uns für
                                    <expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklich</expan></add> drey tag geleyt
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ewr <add>antwurt</add> hören.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
